newid: 1001, date: 3-MAR-1987 09:18:21.26, title: SANDOZ PLANS WEEDKILLER JOINT VENTURE IN USSR, dateline: BASLE, March 3 -, body:  Sandoz AG said it planned a joint venture
to produce herbicides in the Soviet Union.
